				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">The exp might very well be limited. BUT, think of how much you are gettin for the bot char per kill compared to how long it would take that char to get it on his/her own. 
<br />

<br />
  Meaning if you can kill them that much faster with the higher lvl toon and not worrying about the exp he/she gets just to get the lower one up to par with your main then I would say group them and kill stuff quicker. You will get more per kill solo but factor in the time it takes to solo compared to how much quicker you can do it with them grouped. 
<br />
 
<br />
  I have tried it with several characters since I'm and ALT junkie(3 accounts with 24 total chars on my main sever alone) I have just recently started to focus on my Beasty alone and my druid bot. Having the druid with the beasty helped get her a few aa and some lvls just having her sit there cast a heal and DS every so often. And pretty quickly as well.
<br />

<br />
